{"tid":6874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[LIHKG] 一人一件柒事","createTime":"2016-11-27T14:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T05:27:07.000Z","uid":27063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc76a1ebc8d452d921144dd0419ebd729fced457","tid":6874,"uid":27063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"話說有次搭地鐵返學 <br />\n東鐵線月台同列車之間條隙咪闊d嘅<br />\n咁我前面有個肥肥地嘅呀婆 <br />\n臨入車之際佢俾條隙kick到<br />\n佢個身一半係月台一半係車廂<br />\n車入面有一個男人同女人都行過去扶佢 但扶唔起<br />\n咁我就幫手扶佢啦 <br />\n呀 點知呢個時候車門就閂 係到嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟<br />\n我唯有行入車廂先 再幫手扶個呀婆<br />\n點知我一野俾呀婆隻腳kick親 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都成個人仆咗落車廂地下！<br />\n仲要係面向地下個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要扶呀婆個兩個人俾人問有無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個下柒到想搵窿捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一次係我同朋友去放狗<br />\n隻狗係雪橇黎 身型都幾大隻<br />\n當時我坐低咗係張櫈到 拎住條狗繩 見隻狗坐咗係到我就拎電話出黎覆一覆message<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知隻雪橇無啦啦向前衝向前跑 我連人帶櫈被佢拖行咗一小段路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後有途人經過見到 唔知佢係有心定無意講得大聲 我聽到佢講：嘩 原來真係拖得郁咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我嘅心路歷程:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd1f2d94a175a906622a8aa795ca97c03ab2cd5","tid":6874,"uid":2569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"去外國用銀仔，兩毫大餅當兩蚊用，個時唔知，條友係咁講話呢個係兩毫，後面成村人排隊望住，最後俾左大紙等佢找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a51f6997f5a7ca474fbe952494